::Hevn::
       "Yes, yes.  Of course not."  He grins mischievously.  "So your place 
or mine."  He stops for a moment and thinks.  "Actually it should probably be 
yours, since I don't actually have a place of my own, or any place at all."  He 
reaches his arm up for some assistance in standing and smiles amicably at 
Blackstorm.
